title: operators/quantized/server -> quantization/server
body_html:
Summary: Any change in server side quantized operator was triggering ios-sanity-check with more than 5 hours testing time. I suspect this was because the operator code was synced with xplat directory. This diff moves server side quantized operators to caffe2/caffe2/quantization/server to avoid this issue.

Differential Revision: D12955420
